Synopsis:
   break

Description:
   Break, like its C counterpart, breaks out of a loop.

Examples:
   @loop = 0
   while (0==0) {                      /* endless loop? */
     @loop++
     if (loop==20) break
   }                                   /* loop only made 20 iterations */

See Also:
   alias(5); continue(5); return(5); for(5); while(4) until

